x_n = \dfrac{F_n}{F_{n+1}} = \dfrac{a^n - b^n}{a^{n+1} - b^{n+1}} = a \cdot\dfrac{a^{2n} - (-1)^n}{a^{2n+2} - (-1)^n} = a \cdot \dfrac{1 - (-1)^na^{-2n}}{a^2 - (-1)^na^{-2n}} \to \dfrac{1}{a}
